{"day":1,"topic":{"title":"Basics of English","emoji":"📚","cefr":"A0","difficulty":"beginner","type":"grammar"},"content":{"explanation":"\n**English ka Basic Structure:**\n\nHindi mein hum kehte hain: **Subject + Verb + Object**\nEnglish mein bhi same hota hai!\n\n🇮🇳 मैं खाना खाता हूँ।\n🇬🇧 **I** eat **food**.\n(Subject = I, Verb = eat, Object = food)\n\n**Simple Present Tense ke 3 Forms:**\n• I/We/You/They → base verb (eat, drink, go)\n• He/She/It → verb + s/es (eats, drinks, goes)\n  ","rules":["I / We / You / They के साथ base verb — \"I eat\", \"We go\"","He / She / It के साथ verb+s — \"He eats\", \"She goes\"","Question बनाने के लिए: Do/Does + subject + base verb?","Negative बनाने के लिए: Subject + do/does + not + base verb","Facts और daily routines के लिए Simple Present use होता है"],"memoryTrick":"**HE-SHE-IT = S ले लिट!** — He/She/It के साथ verb में S जोड़ दो। बाकी सब (I, We, You, They) base form।","examples":[{"hindi":"मैं पानी पीता हूँ।","english":"I drink water.","type":"Daily Routine"},{"hindi":"वह स्कूल जाती है।","english":"She goes to school.","type":"Daily Routine"},{"hindi":"सूरज पूर्व से उगता है।","english":"The sun rises in the east.","type":"Fact"},{"hindi":"क्या तुम चाय पीते हो?","english":"Do you drink tea?","type":"Question"},{"hindi":"वह खाना नहीं खाती।","english":"She does not eat food.","type":"Negative"},{"hindi":"हम रोज़ पढ़ते हैं।","english":"We study every day.","type":"Habit"}],"mistakes":[{"wrong":"He eat rice.","correct":"He eats rice.","why":"He/She/It के साथ verb+s लगता है"},{"wrong":"I am go to school.","correct":"I go to school.","why":"\"Am\" और base verb साथ नहीं आते"},{"wrong":"She don't like it.","correct":"She doesn't like it.","why":"She के साथ doesn't (does not)"},{"wrong":"Does he goes?","correct":"Does he go?","why":"Does के बाद base verb (no +s)"}],"speakingTips":["रोज़ 5 sentences simple present में बोलने की आदत बनाओ","अपनी daily routine को English में describe करो","\"I wake up, I brush my teeth, I eat breakfast...\" — इस तरह practice करो"]},"vocabulary":[{"id":1,"word":"Usually","hindi":"आमतौर पर","ipa":"","example":"I usually wake up at 7."},{"id":2,"word":"Always","hindi":"हमेशा","ipa":"","example":"She always helps others."},{"id":3,"word":"Often","hindi":"अक्सर","ipa":"","example":"They often play cricket."},{"id":4,"word":"Sometimes","hindi":"कभी-कभी","ipa":"","example":"He sometimes cooks food."},{"id":5,"word":"Never","hindi":"कभी नहीं","ipa":"","example":"I never lie."},{"id":6,"word":"Rarely","hindi":"शायद ही","ipa":"","example":"She rarely goes out."},{"id":7,"word":"Daily","hindi":"रोज़","ipa":"","example":"We exercise daily."},{"id":8,"word":"Frequently","hindi":"बार-बार","ipa":"","example":"He frequently travels."}],"practice":[{"id":"d01-001","hindi":"मैं पानी पीता हूँ।","english":"I drink water.","alternatives":["i drink water"],"hint":"Subject + Verb + Object","explanation":""},{"id":"d01-002","hindi":"वह खाना खाती है।","english":"She eats food.","alternatives":["she eats food."],"hint":"She/He + verb+s","explanation":""},{"id":"d01-003","hindi":"हम स्कूल जाते हैं।","english":"We go to school.","alternatives":["we go to school."],"hint":"We + base verb","explanation":""},{"id":"d01-004","hindi":"वे क्रिकेट खेलते हैं।","english":"They play cricket.","alternatives":["they play cricket."],"hint":"They + base verb","explanation":""},{"id":"d01-005","hindi":"मेरी माँ खाना बनाती है।","english":"My mother cooks food.","alternatives":["my mother cooks food.","my mom cooks food."],"hint":"Singular subject + verb+s","explanation":""},{"id":"d01-006","hindi":"मैं हर रोज़ व्यायाम करता हूँ।","english":"I exercise every day.","alternatives":["i exercise everyday.","i exercise every day."],"hint":"Daily routine = simple present","explanation":""},{"id":"d01-007","hindi":"वह किताब पढ़ता है।","english":"He reads a book.","alternatives":["he reads book.","he reads a book."],"hint":"He + reads (verb+s)","explanation":""},{"id":"d01-008","hindi":"तुम बहुत तेज़ दौड़ते हो।","english":"You run very fast.","alternatives":["you run very fast."],"hint":"You + base verb","explanation":""},{"id":"d01-009","hindi":"बच्चे खेलते हैं।","english":"Children play.","alternatives":["children play.","the children play."],"hint":"Plural = base verb (no +s)","explanation":""},{"id":"d01-010","hindi":"सूरज पूर्व से उगता है।","english":"The sun rises in the east.","alternatives":["sun rises in east.","the sun rises in east."],"hint":"Fact/truth = simple present","explanation":""},{"id":"d01-011","hindi":"मैं चाय पीता हूँ।","english":"I drink tea.","alternatives":["i drink tea."],"hint":"I + base verb","explanation":""},{"id":"d01-012","hindi":"वह ऑफिस जाती है।","english":"She goes to the office.","alternatives":["she goes to office.","she goes to the office."],"hint":"She + goes (irregular verb+s)","explanation":""},{"id":"d01-013","hindi":"मेरा भाई गाना गाता है।","english":"My brother sings a song.","alternatives":["my brother sings songs."],"hint":"Singular + verb+s","explanation":""},{"id":"d01-014","hindi":"कुत्ते भौंकते हैं।","english":"Dogs bark.","alternatives":["dogs bark.","the dogs bark."],"hint":"Plural noun + base verb","explanation":""},{"id":"d01-015","hindi":"मैं अंग्रेज़ी सीखता हूँ।","english":"I learn English.","alternatives":["i study english.","i am learning english."],"hint":"I + base verb","explanation":""},{"id":"d01-016","hindi":"वे हर दिन काम करते हैं।","english":"They work every day.","alternatives":["they work everyday.","they work every day."],"hint":"They + base verb","explanation":""},{"id":"d01-017","hindi":"मेरे दोस्त मेरी मदद करते हैं।","english":"My friends help me.","alternatives":["my friends help me."],"hint":"Plural subject + base verb","explanation":""},{"id":"d01-018","hindi":"पक्षी आकाश में उड़ते हैं।","english":"Birds fly in the sky.","alternatives":["birds fly in sky.","birds fly in the sky."],"hint":"Plural + base verb","explanation":""},{"id":"d01-019","hindi":"मैं सुबह जल्दी उठता हूँ।","english":"I wake up early in the morning.","alternatives":["i wake up early morning.","i get up early in the morning."],"hint":"I + base verb","explanation":""},{"id":"d01-020","hindi":"वह बहुत खुश रहती है।","english":"She stays very happy.","alternatives":["she is very happy.","she remains very happy."],"hint":"She + stays/is + adjective","explanation":""},{"id":"d01-021","hindi":"पानी ऊपर से नीचे बहता है।","english":"Water flows from top to bottom.","alternatives":["water flows downward."],"hint":"Scientific fact = simple present","explanation":""},{"id":"d01-022","hindi":"मेरे पिता अखबार पढ़ते हैं।","english":"My father reads the newspaper.","alternatives":["my father reads newspaper."],"hint":"Singular subject + reads","explanation":""},{"id":"d01-023","hindi":"हम मिलकर काम करते हैं।","english":"We work together.","alternatives":["we work together."],"hint":"We + base verb","explanation":""},{"id":"d01-024","hindi":"वह रात को देर से सोता है।","english":"He sleeps late at night.","alternatives":["he sleeps late at night."],"hint":"He + sleeps","explanation":""},{"id":"d01-025","hindi":"मेरी बहन नृत्य करती है।","english":"My sister dances.","alternatives":["my sister dances.","my sister dance."],"hint":"Singular + verb+s","explanation":""},{"id":"d01-026","hindi":"बादल आकाश में उड़ते हैं।","english":"Clouds float in the sky.","alternatives":["clouds float in sky."],"hint":"Plural + base verb","explanation":""},{"id":"d01-027","hindi":"मैं रोज़ नहाता हूँ।","english":"I take a bath every day.","alternatives":["i bathe every day.","i shower every day."],"hint":"Daily habit = simple present","explanation":""},{"id":"d01-028","hindi":"मेरे शिक्षक अच्छे हैं।","english":"My teachers are good.","alternatives":["my teachers are good."],"hint":"Plural + are","explanation":""},{"id":"d01-029","hindi":"वह बहुत मेहनत करता है।","english":"He works very hard.","alternatives":["he works hard."],"hint":"He + works (with +s)","explanation":""},{"id":"d01-030","hindi":"हम सब दोस्त हैं।","english":"We are all friends.","alternatives":["we all are friends."],"hint":"We + are","explanation":""},{"id":"d01-031","hindi":"वह बस पकड़ता है।","english":"He catches the bus.","alternatives":["he takes the bus."],"hint":"He + catches (verb+s)","explanation":""},{"id":"d01-032","hindi":"मेरी दादी कहानियाँ सुनाती हैं।","english":"My grandmother tells stories.","alternatives":["my grandma tells stories."],"hint":"Singular + tells (verb+s)","explanation":""},{"id":"d01-033","hindi":"वे सब्ज़ियाँ खाते हैं।","english":"They eat vegetables.","alternatives":["they eat veggies."],"hint":"They + base verb","explanation":""},{"id":"d01-034","hindi":"मैं संगीत सुनता हूँ।","english":"I listen to music.","alternatives":["i love listening to music."],"hint":"I + listen to","explanation":""},{"id":"d01-035","hindi":"वह मुझे रोज़ फ़ोन करता है।","english":"He calls me every day.","alternatives":["he phones me daily."],"hint":"He + calls (verb+s)","explanation":""},{"id":"d01-036","hindi":"बिल्ली दूध पीती है।","english":"The cat drinks milk.","alternatives":["cats drink milk."],"hint":"Singular noun + verb+s","explanation":""},{"id":"d01-037","hindi":"हम रोज़ अख़बार पढ़ते हैं।","english":"We read the newspaper every day.","alternatives":["we read the paper daily."],"hint":"We + base verb","explanation":""},{"id":"d01-038","hindi":"मेरे नाना खेत में काम करते हैं।","english":"My grandfather works in the field.","alternatives":["my grandpa works on the farm."],"hint":"Singular + works (verb+s)","explanation":""},{"id":"d01-039","hindi":"वह अपने कमरे को साफ़ रखती है।","english":"She keeps her room clean.","alternatives":["she keeps her room tidy."],"hint":"She + keeps (verb+s)","explanation":""},{"id":"d01-040","hindi":"बच्चे स्कूल में पढ़ते हैं।","english":"Children study in school.","alternatives":["kids study at school."],"hint":"Plural + base verb","explanation":""},{"id":"d01-041","hindi":"मेरा कुत्ता हड्डी खाता है।","english":"My dog eats bones.","alternatives":["my dog chews bones."],"hint":"My dog + eats (verb+s)","explanation":""},{"id":"d01-042","hindi":"मैं हर शाम टहलता हूँ।","english":"I walk every evening.","alternatives":["i go for a walk every evening."],"hint":"I + base verb + time","explanation":""},{"id":"d01-043","hindi":"वह बहुत मीठा खाती है।","english":"She eats a lot of sweets.","alternatives":["she loves sweet food."],"hint":"She + eats (verb+s)","explanation":""},{"id":"d01-044","hindi":"हमारी टीम जीतती है।","english":"Our team wins.","alternatives":["our team always wins."],"hint":"Our team + wins (verb+s)","explanation":""},{"id":"d01-045","hindi":"मछलियाँ पानी में तैरती हैं।","english":"Fish swim in water.","alternatives":["fish live in water."],"hint":"Plural + base verb","explanation":""},{"id":"d01-046","hindi":"वह हिंदी और अंग्रेज़ी बोलता है।","english":"He speaks Hindi and English.","alternatives":["he knows hindi and english."],"hint":"He + speaks (verb+s)","explanation":""},{"id":"d01-047","hindi":"मेरी माँ सुबह जल्दी उठती हैं।","english":"My mother wakes up early in the morning.","alternatives":["my mom gets up early."],"hint":"Singular + wakes up (verb+s)","explanation":""},{"id":"d01-048","hindi":"वे साथ में खाना खाते हैं।","english":"They eat together.","alternatives":["they have meals together."],"hint":"They + base verb","explanation":""},{"id":"d01-049","hindi":"चाँद रात में चमकता है।","english":"The moon shines at night.","alternatives":["the moon glows at night."],"hint":"Fact = simple present","explanation":""},{"id":"d01-050","hindi":"मैं दूध पीता हूँ।","english":"I drink milk.","alternatives":["i have milk."],"hint":"I + base verb","explanation":""},{"id":"d01-051","hindi":"मेरे दोस्त मेरे साथ खेलते हैं।","english":"My friends play with me.","alternatives":["my friends play along with me."],"hint":"Plural + base verb","explanation":""},{"id":"d01-052","hindi":"वह हर सुबह योगा करती है।","english":"She does yoga every morning.","alternatives":["she practices yoga every morning."],"hint":"She + does (verb+s)","explanation":""},{"id":"d01-053","hindi":"मैं रात में किताब पढ़ता हूँ।","english":"I read a book at night.","alternatives":["i read books at night."],"hint":"I + base verb","explanation":""},{"id":"d01-054","hindi":"शेर जंगल में रहते हैं।","english":"Lions live in the forest.","alternatives":["lions stay in the jungle."],"hint":"Plural + base verb","explanation":""},{"id":"d01-055","hindi":"मेरे पिता सुबह अख़बार पढ़ते हैं।","english":"My father reads the newspaper in the morning.","alternatives":["my dad reads the paper every morning."],"hint":"Singular + reads (verb+s)","explanation":""},{"id":"d01-056","hindi":"वे हर रविवार चर्च जाते हैं।","english":"They go to church every Sunday.","alternatives":["they attend church on sundays."],"hint":"They + base verb","explanation":""},{"id":"d01-057","hindi":"मेरा बेटा फुटबॉल खेलता है।","english":"My son plays football.","alternatives":["my son plays soccer."],"hint":"Singular + plays (verb+s)","explanation":""},{"id":"d01-058","hindi":"हम सब मिलकर पढ़ते हैं।","english":"We all study together.","alternatives":["we study together as a group."],"hint":"We + base verb","explanation":""},{"id":"d01-059","hindi":"वह हर रात 8 बजे सो जाती है।","english":"She sleeps at 8 every night.","alternatives":["she goes to bed at 8 pm every night."],"hint":"She + sleeps (verb+s)","explanation":""},{"id":"d01-060","hindi":"पत्ते पेड़ से गिरते हैं।","english":"Leaves fall from trees.","alternatives":["leaves drop from trees."],"hint":"Plural + base verb (natural fact)","explanation":""},{"id":"d01-061","hindi":"मैं सब्ज़ी बाज़ार से लाता हूँ।","english":"I buy vegetables from the market.","alternatives":["i get vegetables from the market."],"hint":"I + base verb + from","explanation":""},{"id":"d01-062","hindi":"वह दफ़्तर में काम करती है।","english":"She works in the office.","alternatives":["she works at the office."],"hint":"She + works (verb+s)","explanation":""},{"id":"d01-063","hindi":"हमारा देश भारत है।","english":"Our country is India.","alternatives":["we live in india."],"hint":"Our country + is","explanation":""},{"id":"d01-064","hindi":"मेरी दीदी नर्स है।","english":"My sister is a nurse.","alternatives":["my elder sister is a nurse."],"hint":"Singular + is + profession","explanation":""},{"id":"d01-065","hindi":"वे बहुत अच्छा गाना गाते हैं।","english":"They sing very well.","alternatives":["they are great singers."],"hint":"They + base verb + adverb","explanation":""},{"id":"d01-066","hindi":"मैं रोज़ सुबह दाँत साफ़ करता हूँ।","english":"I brush my teeth every morning.","alternatives":["i clean my teeth every morning."],"hint":"Daily routine = simple present","explanation":""},{"id":"d01-067","hindi":"वह बहुत तेज़ बोलता है।","english":"He speaks very fast.","alternatives":["he talks very fast."],"hint":"He + speaks (verb+s) + adverb","explanation":""},{"id":"d01-068","hindi":"मेरी माँ मुझसे बहुत प्यार करती है।","english":"My mother loves me very much.","alternatives":["my mom loves me a lot."],"hint":"Singular + loves (verb+s)","explanation":""},{"id":"d01-069","hindi":"हाथी बहुत बड़े होते हैं।","english":"Elephants are very big.","alternatives":["elephants are huge animals."],"hint":"Plural + are + adjective (fact)","explanation":""},{"id":"d01-070","hindi":"मैं हर दिन कुछ नया सीखता हूँ।","english":"I learn something new every day.","alternatives":["i try to learn something new daily."],"hint":"I + base verb","explanation":""},{"id":"d01-071","hindi":"वह अपने परिवार के साथ रहती है।","english":"She lives with her family.","alternatives":["she stays with her family."],"hint":"She + lives (verb+s)","explanation":""},{"id":"d01-072","hindi":"मेरा दोस्त बहुत हँसमुख है।","english":"My friend is very cheerful.","alternatives":["my friend is always happy."],"hint":"Singular + is + adjective","explanation":""},{"id":"d01-073","hindi":"वे कभी-कभी सिनेमा जाते हैं।","english":"They sometimes go to the cinema.","alternatives":["they sometimes watch movies."],"hint":"They + base verb + sometimes","explanation":""},{"id":"d01-074","hindi":"मैं सुबह चाय पीता हूँ।","english":"I drink tea in the morning.","alternatives":["i have tea every morning."],"hint":"I + base verb","explanation":""},{"id":"d01-075","hindi":"वह हर सुबह दौड़ता है।","english":"He runs every morning.","alternatives":["he jogs every morning."],"hint":"He + runs (verb+s)","explanation":""},{"id":"d01-076","hindi":"मेरे भाई की नौकरी बैंक में है।","english":"My brother works in a bank.","alternatives":["my brother has a job at a bank."],"hint":"Singular + works (verb+s)","explanation":""},{"id":"d01-077","hindi":"बच्चे मिठाई पसंद करते हैं।","english":"Children like sweets.","alternatives":["kids love candy."],"hint":"Plural + base verb","explanation":""},{"id":"d01-078","hindi":"वह खूब मेहनत करता है।","english":"He works very hard.","alternatives":["he puts in a lot of effort."],"hint":"He + works (verb+s)","explanation":""},{"id":"d01-079","hindi":"हम रोज़ घर की सफ़ाई करते हैं।","english":"We clean the house every day.","alternatives":["we tidy up the house daily."],"hint":"We + base verb","explanation":""},{"id":"d01-080","hindi":"गाय घास खाती है।","english":"The cow eats grass.","alternatives":["cows eat grass."],"hint":"Singular + eats (verb+s)","explanation":""},{"id":"d01-081","hindi":"मैं अपने दोस्तों के साथ क्रिकेट खेलता हूँ।","english":"I play cricket with my friends.","alternatives":["i play cricket with friends."],"hint":"I + base verb","explanation":""},{"id":"d01-082","hindi":"मेरी बहन हर शाम गाती है।","english":"My sister sings every evening.","alternatives":["my sister sings in the evenings."],"hint":"Singular + sings (verb+s)","explanation":""},{"id":"d01-083","hindi":"वे हर साल पहाड़ों पर जाते हैं।","english":"They go to the mountains every year.","alternatives":["they visit the mountains annually."],"hint":"They + base verb + time","explanation":""},{"id":"d01-084","hindi":"मैं खाने के बाद हाथ धोता हूँ।","english":"I wash my hands after eating.","alternatives":["i clean my hands after meals."],"hint":"Daily habit = simple present","explanation":""},{"id":"d01-085","hindi":"नदी समुद्र में मिलती है।","english":"The river meets the sea.","alternatives":["rivers flow into the ocean."],"hint":"Scientific fact = simple present","explanation":""},{"id":"d01-086","hindi":"वह अपनी माँ की मदद करती है।","english":"She helps her mother.","alternatives":["she assists her mom."],"hint":"She + helps (verb+s)","explanation":""},{"id":"d01-087","hindi":"मेरे चाचा डॉक्टर हैं।","english":"My uncle is a doctor.","alternatives":["my uncle works as a doctor."],"hint":"Singular + is + profession","explanation":""},{"id":"d01-088","hindi":"हम सब भारत से प्यार करते हैं।","english":"We all love India.","alternatives":["we all love our country."],"hint":"We + base verb","explanation":""},{"id":"d01-089","hindi":"वह हमेशा समय पर आता है।","english":"He always comes on time.","alternatives":["he is always punctual."],"hint":"He + comes (verb+s) + always","explanation":""},{"id":"d01-090","hindi":"तोते रंग-बिरंगे होते हैं।","english":"Parrots are colourful.","alternatives":["parrots have colourful feathers."],"hint":"Plural + are + adjective (fact)","explanation":""},{"id":"d01-091","hindi":"मैं हर हफ्ते बाज़ार जाता हूँ।","english":"I go to the market every week.","alternatives":["i visit the market weekly."],"hint":"I + base verb","explanation":""},{"id":"d01-092","hindi":"वह रोज़ शाम को टहलती है।","english":"She goes for a walk every evening.","alternatives":["she takes a walk in the evenings."],"hint":"She + goes (verb+s)","explanation":""},{"id":"d01-093","hindi":"मेरे दोस्त बास्केटबॉल खेलते हैं।","english":"My friends play basketball.","alternatives":["my friends enjoy playing basketball."],"hint":"Plural + base verb","explanation":""},{"id":"d01-094","hindi":"कमल पानी में खिलता है।","english":"The lotus blooms in water.","alternatives":["lotuses grow in water."],"hint":"Natural fact = simple present","explanation":""},{"id":"d01-095","hindi":"मैं अपना कमरा रोज़ साफ़ करता हूँ।","english":"I c