ots have colourful feathers."]},{"id":"d01-091-test","hindi":"मैं हर हफ्ते बाज़ार जाता हूँ।","english":"I go to the market every week.","alternatives":["i visit the market weekly."]},{"id":"d01-092-test","hindi":"वह रोज़ शाम को टहलती है।","english":"She goes for a walk every evening.","alternatives":["she takes a walk in the evenings."]},{"id":"d01-093-test","hindi":"मेरे दोस्त बास्केटबॉल खेलते हैं।","english":"My friends play basketball.","alternatives":["my friends enjoy playing basketball."]},{"id":"d01-094-test","hindi":"कमल पानी में खिलता है।","english":"The lotus blooms in water.","alternatives":["lotuses grow in water."]},{"id":"d01-095-test","hindi":"मैं अपना कमरा रोज़ साफ़ करता हूँ।","english":"I clean my room every day.","alternatives":["i tidy my room daily."]},{"id":"d01-096-test","hindi":"वह बहुत कम बोलता है।","english":"He speaks very little.","alternatives":["he is a man of few words."]},{"id":"d01-097-test","hindi":"मेरी कक्षा में 40 छात्र हैं।","english":"There are 40 students in my class.","alternatives":["my class has 40 students."]},{"id":"d01-098-test","hindi":"हम सब खाना मिलकर खाते हैं।","english":"We all eat together.","alternatives":["we have meals together."]},{"id":"d01-099-test","hindi":"वह स्कूल में पढ़ाती है।","english":"She teaches in school.","alternatives":["she is a school teacher."]},{"id":"d01-100-test","hindi":"मैं रोज़ रात 10 बजे सोता हूँ।","english":"I sleep at 10 pm every night.","alternatives":["i go to bed at 10 every night."]},{"id":"d01-101-test","hindi":"मेरे पड़ोसी बहुत अच्छे हैं।","english":"My neighbours are very nice.","alternatives":["my neighbors are very good people."]},{"id":"d01-102-test","hindi":"वह अपने बच्चों को पढ़ाता है।","english":"He teaches his children.","alternatives":["he educates his kids."]}]}